item.title: Official Samsung Black USB-C to USB-C Cable 1.8m
item.dc:creator: quickmoney
item.description:
• Official Samsung Cable
  • Compatible with all USB-C Devices
  • Fast data transfer
  • 1.8-metre cable length
  • Tested to be compliant with USB-C to USB-C standards
item.content:encoded:
The internet is flooded with cheap fake Samsung chargers and cables that could damage your phone and possibly even cause injury to yourself and your family. At Mobile Fun, we pride ourselves on only sourcing products from respected suppliers that have been authorised by Samsung. So, you can be sure of a top-quality accessory that has been manufactured to Samsung’s recognised quality assurance for the best compatibility and most important of all – the best safety standards

Compatible with all USB-C Devices

The 1.8m cable is compatible with all devices with a USB-C connector. With more and more devices now coming with the USB-C connection, this cable is able to provide your phone with blistering transfer and charging speeds. With USB-C can you never plug the connector in the wrong way, no more battling with your charging cable in the dark!

Fast data transfer

Suitable for syncing data between your phone and computer, this cable provides extreme transfer speeds that allow you to quickly copy pictures, movies and much more.

1.8-metre cable length

This Official Samsung USB-C cable is 1.8 metres in length, allowing you to comfortably charge and sync your device without having to worry about stretching and damaging the cable.

Tested to be compliant with USB-C to USB-C standards

This cable has been tested to be compliant with the USB-C to USB-C standard. Non-compliant cables can attempt to draw as much as 3 amps (3A), which could potentially damage connected equipment when they are not compatible with this high power output.

Don’t take the risk, as the Official Samsung Black 3A USB-C to USB-C Cable has been tested to ensure it’s compliant with USB-C to USB-C standards.

What’s in the box?

  • 1 x Official Samsung Black 3A USB-C to USB-C Cable 1.8m

item.title: Official OnePlus Warp Charge 1m USB-C to USB-C Charging Cable
item.dc:creator: quickmoney
item.description:
• Official OnePlus Accessory
  • Super-Fast charging with a maximum of 65W
  • USB-C Power Delivery Compatible
  • 1 Meter (100cm) Cable Length
  • Fast data transfer speed for accessing and copying files
  • Compatible with all USB-C Devices
item.content:encoded:
Official OnePlus Accessory

The internet is flooded with cheap fake chargers and cables that could damage your phone and possibly even cause injury. At Mobile Fun, we pride ourselves on only sourcing products from respected suppliers that have been authorised by OnePlus. So, you can be sure of a top quality accessory that has been manufactured to the recognised standards and quality assurance for the best compatibility and most important of all – the best safety standards. With this cable being made directly by OnePlus you can rest assured knowing this is a top-quality product for your OnePlus or another android device!

Power Delivery Compatible

This Official OnePlus cable offers fast USB-C power delivery. The internal cabling is comprised of high-grade copper and nickel, whilst the outside is coated in a premium silicone coating to ensure a smooth and efficient safe power delivery to your OnePlus (or other USB-C) smartphone. The OnePlus cable is a reversible Type-C connector and utilises a separate injection process further strengthening connector pins. Enjoy up to 65W of Warp charge speed – revolutionise your charging!

1 Metre (100cm) Cable Length

This cable is 1 metre long, with a low profile and slim design making it perfect for not only charging but also data transfer and syncing whether at home in the office or on the go.

Fast data transfer speed for accessing and copying files

Suitable for syncing data between your two devices, this cable provides extreme transfer speeds that allows you to quickly copy pictures, movies and much more anytime anywhere!

Compatible with all USB-C Devices

The official Oneplus cable is compatible with warp charger 30 technology and is compatible with most OnePlus devices such as: OnePlus Nord N100, OnePlus N10 5G, OnePlus 8 Pro, OnePlus 8, OnePlus 7 Pro, OnePlus 7, OnePlus 6T, OnePlus 6, OnePlus 5T, OnePlus 5, OnePlus 3T and OnePlus 3.

What’s in the box?

  • 1 x Official OnePlus Warp Charge 1m USB-C to USB-C Charging Cable
